  "informal_statement": "If three points have equal slopes from the first (collinear), the signed-area determinant is zero.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "The determinant is exactly the negation of the slope-equality residual; `linear_combination -h`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem collinear_det (x1 y1 x2 y2 x3 y3 : ℝ) (h : (y2 - y1) * (x3 - x1) = (y3 - y1) * (x2 - x1)) : (x2 - x1) * (y3 - y1) - (x3 - x1) * (y2 - y1) = 0",
